    "display_name": "Design a Word Puzzle",
    "long_instructions": "## Design a Word Puzzle\r\n\r\n**Before You Start:**\r\n\r\nMake sure you have filled in the **K** and **W** columns of your KWL chart for this task.\r\n\r\n**Do:**\r\n\r\nAsk AI to create a word puzzle (like a crossword, word search, or riddle) based on a topic you choose.\r\n\r\n**Try:**\r\n\r\nGive it a theme, like science terms, school supplies, or pop culture, and see how well it follows it.\r\n\r\n**Check:**\r\n\r\nAre the clues accurate and clear? Does the puzzle follow real rules?\r\n\r\n**After You Try It:**\r\n\r\n1. Fill in the **L** column of your KWL chart\r\n\r\n2. Press **Continue** to return to the task menu\r\n",
